Navigation Drawer For Movie Detail : ->Added code to display login item in Nav Drawer If User Not Logged In ->Increased the DB Version number for pre-14 version compatability. ->Provided translatable strings for NavDrawer Item Titles.

Animation Code Added: Animated View : Login Activity Next Steps Circular Card View
Upon Login the user clicks the View element and the Circular Card View Explodes and encompases the entire screen. After the Animation Ends , JVM calls the onAnimationEnd() overriden method in the listener and an Intent is dispatched to start a new Activity.
